{"tid":1348043,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家驚還驚 都要理下屯元天居民嘅安全","createTime":"2019-07-22T07:21:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T10:42:54.000Z","uid":215700,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3cdd15c01502a9c20154810222df250e59a9e45b","tid":1348043,"uid":215700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:21:40.000Z","msg":"由今朝開始已經收到無數未fact check嘅消息 大家擔心驚係正常 <br />\n我地依刻要做嘅係提醒屯元天居民盡快返屋企 而唔係不斷share fake news製造白色恐怖<br />\n<br />\n有唔少住當地嘅巴打 都打算落樓護送下街坊返屋企 保護下記者 你地不斷放fake news製造白色恐怖只會影響到我地 對件事無幫助 <br />\n<br />\n依刻要做嘅係提醒等陣放工要返屯元天嘅同事朋友親戚小心 盡可能就接濟下佢地 提醒佢地依家好危險<br />\n<br />\n屯元天人口好多 唔會單單半日就全部居民知道依個消息 就算去到入夜都一定仲有依班市民 係現場 <br />\n承擔到風險嘅巴打就盡量護送<br />\n普通市民就提醒屯元天嘅朋友 得嘅就接濟佢地/送佢地返屋企<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好白色恐怖</span></span>"},{"pid":"73f7d260197e7d81872daabca1a94a9bb252e014","tid":1348043,"uid":215700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:22:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3985ea1972f577ba47328a7c727e721b766b1cd9","tid":1348043,"uid":215700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:23:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e293dd436bf02fc067d7cfd97320d08029be383f","tid":1348043,"uid":215700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:23:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27c641fd00e177c91eb69bfa5b7f2b1714f81a37","tid":1348043,"uid":248470,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:23:47.000Z","msg":"建制派及其政府 公然向香港市民發動恐怖襲擊！<br />\n<br />\n地鐵故意堅持開住車箱門，任由警黑合作虐打市民<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港政府= 台灣鄭捷"},{"pid":"225b2eaefce0397f6399eee3c2ffb14b193d6e85","tid":1348043,"uid":215700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:24:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" 